"If presenting tomorrow, what would I change first?"

Wire webhook delivery into the scan proc for CRITICAL events. One CALL SYSTEM$SEND_NOTIFICATION(...) or a simple HTTP-based notification integration. The detection is now solid; the last mile is delivery. An exec will ask "so when something critical happens at 2am, who gets paged?" and right now the answer is "nobody, until they open the app."

